items.title: Shortest remaining time - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Shortest remaining time - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
Shortest remaining time, also known as shortest remaining time first (SRTF), is a 
scheduling method that is a preemptive version of shortest job next scheduling.
